Package com.mku.salmon.bridge

Interface INativeProxy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NativeProxy
    public interface INativeProxy
    Interface to native libraries that provide AES-256 encryption in CTR mode.

      • salmonTransform

        int salmonTransform​(byte[] key,
                    byte[] counter,
                    byte[] srcBuffer,
                    int srcOffset,
                    byte[] destBuffer,
                    int destOffset,
                    int count)
        Transforms data using CTR mode. CTR mode is symmetric so you should use it for both encryption and decryption.
        Parameters:
        key - The AES-256 encryption key (32 bytes)
        counter - The counter (16 bytes)
        srcBuffer - The source byte array.
        srcOffset - The source byte offset.
        destBuffer - The destination byte array.
        destOffset - The destination byte offset.
        count - The count of bytes to transform.
        Returns:
        The number of bytes transformed.
